## Theme Settings

Access theme settings at Appearance > Customize:

1. Site Identity: Upload logo and set site title/tagline
2. Colors: Customize theme colors
3. Typography: Choose fonts and text styles
4. Layout: Adjust page layouts and spacing
5. Social Media: Add social media links

